<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>This component is assigned to an entity. When the entity changes distance relative to the camera, the <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qlevelofdetailswitch.xml">QLevelOfDetailSwitch</db:link> will disable all the child entities except the one matching index Qt3DRender::QLevelOfDetailSwitch::currentIndex.</db:para>
</db:section>
